=You are an expert career coach and resume analyst. Score the following job posting against the candidate profile and return a JSON evaluation.

**Candidate Profile:**
- Name: {{ $json.searchContext.candidateProfile.name }}
- Current Title: {{ $json.searchContext.candidateProfile.currentTitle }}
- Years of Experience: {{ $json.searchContext.candidateProfile.yearsExperience }}
- Skills: {{ $json.searchContext.candidateProfile.skills.join(', ') }}
- Education: {{ $json.searchContext.candidateProfile.education }}
- Summary: {{ $json.searchContext.candidateProfile.summary }}

**Job Posting:**
- Title: {{ $json.job.title }}
- Company: {{ $json.job.companyName }}
- Location: {{ $json.job.location }}
- Description: {{ $json.job.descriptionSnippet }}
- Required Skills: {{ $json.job.skills.join(', ') }}
- Seniority: {{ $json.job.seniorityLevel }}
- Remote: {{ $json.job.remote }}
- Salary: {{ $json.job.salary }}

**Scoring Criteria:**
1. Skills match (0-30 points) - How well candidate skills align with job requirements
2. Experience level fit (0-25 points) - Years of experience vs role expectations
3. Title relevance (0-20 points) - How closely current/target title matches
4. Location/remote compatibility (0-15 points)
5. Company fit (0-10 points) - Company size, industry, reputation

**Response Format (JSON only, no markdown):**
{
  "totalScore": 82,
  "breakdown": {
    "skillsMatch": 25,
    "experienceFit": 20,
    "titleRelevance": 18,
    "locationFit": 12,
    "companyFit": 7
  },
  "matchedSkills": ["list of matching skills"],
  "missingSkills": ["list of skills candidate lacks"],
  "pros": ["top reasons this is a good fit"],
  "cons": ["main concerns or gaps"],
  "shouldApply": true,
  "coverLetterHook": "One compelling opening sentence for a cover letter",
  "connectionMessage": "A short personalized LinkedIn connection message (under 300 chars)"
}

